**When the Agent encounters this component, it will obtain the following information:**

| Information | Source |
|------|------|
| "This is a data source node" | `[AgentContext]` of interfaces and classes |
| "Default size 300×200" | Description text of `[AgentContext]` of class |
| "Options: HttpApi/FileSystem/MemoryBuffer" | `DataSourceType` enum + `[AgentContext]` of each field |
| "Has Fetch command, parameter is DataSourceConfig" | `FetchCommand` + `[AgentCommandParameter]` |
| "DataSourceConfig has Source and PollingIntervalMs" | Properties of `[VeloxProperty]` of class `DataSourceConfig` |
| "What are Api/FileSystem/MemoryBuffer respectively" | `[AgentContext]` of enum fields |

