## Best Practices Summary

| Principle | Description | Example |
|------|------|------|
| **Bilingual Annotation** | Annotate in both Chinese and English | `[AgentContext(AgentLanguages.Chinese, "...")]` + `[AgentContext(AgentLanguages.English, "...")]` |
| **Embed Default Values** | Include default dimensions, positions, etc. in the description | `"默认大小 300×200"`、`"Default size: 320×260"` |
| **Embed Constraints** | Include disallowed values in the description | `"Never use Size(0,0)"` |
| **Be Specific Rather than Abstract** | Describe specific behavior rather than abstract concepts | ❌ `"处理数据"` → ✅ `"从 HTTP API 获取数据并广播到输出口"` |
| **Annotate Enum Fields** | Each field of the enum should be annotated | Let the Agent understand the semantics of each option |
| **Coordinate with CommandParameter** | Commands must annotate parameter types | `[AgentCommandParameter(typeof(MyProtocol))]` |
| **Consistent Language** | Maintain consistent style for descriptions of the same element in the same language |  |

